{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5ec2d5b28c","title":"同济大学右派分子反对无产阶级专政的言论","origin":"同济大学马列主义资料室编印《右派分子言论汇编》第二辑（内部资料不得外传），一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ac210ee96a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"98f03a4072","name":"同济大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"57543ee4a2","type":"title","text":"同济大学右派分子反对无产阶级专政的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"ba4dbd7cf5","type":"authors","text":"同济大学","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"97e76f86e4","type":"paragraph","text":"城建系助教  李铮生","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"505d8aa692","type":"paragraph","text":"“各种运动破坏了人与人正常关系。”并歪曲说：“我们的社会就没有人情味。”（见校刊129期第四版）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"5cd8464cf9","type":"paragraph","text":"校刊编辑室职员  唐玉白","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"b3d696c1b6","type":"paragraph","text":"“社会主义的光芒，我胆怯、心慌、眼花。”“别人幸福的死去，我却痛苦的生存。”（见校刊131期第六版）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"80b97adfab","type":"paragraph","text":"速中语文教师  余力容","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"f881573980","type":"paragraph","text":"“无产阶级专政是‘一党专政’，民主党派没有自己的斗争纲领，是共产党的花瓶。”（见校刊119期第六版）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"35f7f93410","type":"paragraph","text":"道桥系毕业生  吴志刚","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"3127fabbe1","type":"paragraph","text":"“官僚主义、个人崇拜是社会主义制度产生的。”（摘自道桥系毕业生吴志刚材料）","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"c6197941a0","type":"paragraph","text":"卫生工程系毕业生  姚骏之","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"758c324a0c","type":"paragraph","text":"“人民政府是捞钞票，要捞人民政府的一分钱都是困难的。”“现在犯人坐牢睡在里面不准讲话否则遭打。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"7a710f0b98","type":"paragraph","text":"造谣说：“南京学生要打报馆，政府动员了三轮车工人将学生打走。”（摘自卫生工程系毕业生姚骏之材料）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"8d47ba5e2e","type":"paragraph","text":"铁路系毕业生  邱镕兆","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"4d8d03235e","type":"paragraph","text":"“说三大主义是社会主义制度的产物，也有道理。”（摘自铁路系毕业生邱镕兆材料）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"a29f590a0f","type":"paragraph","text":"城建系毕业生  史奉羔","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"c0b3f378dd","type":"paragraph","text":"反胡风学习在本校开展时他说：“胡风你们认得吗？不认得不要讲。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"a674527df6","type":"paragraph","text":"在公布胡风材料时，有一句‘胡风在日本有一段时期是干了不可告人的勾当。’他说：“胡风既然干了不可告人的勾当，你们又不知道。”（意思是指人民日报报道空洞）。（摘自城建系毕业生史奉羔材料）","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"969c50ea3a","type":"paragraph","text":"结构系毕业生  周知其","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"44c0fd0867","type":"paragraph","text":"“我作为一个人民和青年群众，我要求国家应该对于每一个公民有法律的保障，要求真正的贯彻民主、平等、自由的政策。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"5658396368","type":"paragraph","text":"“为什么仅仅因为一个青年偶犯了一些错误和思想上不符（你们的）要求，就要给他种种打击，甚至几乎要迫他走上绝路呢。这难道是革命的目的吗？”（摘自结构系毕业生周知其材料）","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"8b52fc8c42","type":"paragraph","text":"道桥系毕业生  吴志刚","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"},{"id":"af83be5cf8","type":"paragraph","text":"他曾写过这样一首仇恨新社会的诗：“我高举起我的葬旗，嘴里哼着哀歌，向前！向前！朝着我的坟墓前进！”（摘自道桥系毕业生吴志刚材料）","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c"}],"page":{"id":"cb63ae9401","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ec2d5b28c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}